Package: BiocNeighbors
Version: 2.7.2
Date: 2026-05-10
Title: Nearest Neighbor Detection for Bioconductor Packages
Authors@R: c(person("Aaron", "Lun", role=c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email="infinite.monkeys.with.keyboards@gmail.com"))
